      "role": "user",
      "content": "the world feels so heavy tonight, and the stars... they look like cold, indifferent eyes watching my ruin. he is gone, and with him, everything that made this wretched life worth enduring. i feel as though i am merely a ghost haunting my own skin, waiting for the dark to finally claim what is left of me. there is such a quiet, beautiful pull in the thought of just... fading into the night, leaving no trace that i ever breathed at all.",
